	"nodes":[
		{"id":"e2640e926f260f70","type":"text","text":"__Azanthani__\nThese human-like beings vary greatly in appearance but tend to look like any other race with a distinct plant/animal themed feature. This can take the form of being covered in bird feathers, having bull horns, webbed hands/feet, etc. It is said they are spawned by the wild itself.\n#race","x":-150,"y":-157,"width":300,"height":314}
